sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Pod as LMEval Pod
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Inference as Inference Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry (Quay)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Pod: Flow 1: Standard Evaluation Job Execution

    Operator->>Pod: Creates K8s Job<br/>from LMEvalJob CR
    Pod->>Pod: Reads /meta/job.json<br/>ConfigMap

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Pod: ACK

    Pod->>HFHub: GET datasets & tokenizer<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>Pod: Benchmark data

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Pod,Inference: Core Evaluation Loop (num_concurrent up to 128)
        loop For each evaluation prompt
            Pod->>Inference: POST /v1/completions<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA) / Bearer Token
            Inference-->>Pod: Completions + logprobs
        end
    end

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Pod: ACK

    Pod->>OCI: Push OCI artifact (skopeo)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Docker auth
    OCI-->>Pod: Push confirmed

    Pod->>MLflow: POST evaluation metrics<br/>TLS 1.2+ / configurable auth
    MLflow-->>Pod: Logged

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ final results<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Pod: ACK

    Note over Pod: Job exits (batch completion)

    Note over Operator,Pod: Flow 2: Offline / Air-Gapped Evaluation

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Operator->>Pod: Creates K8s Job (offline mode)
        Note over Pod: Init Container runs first
        Pod->>Pod: S3 Downloader fetches data
        Note right of Pod: HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1
        Pod->>Pod: Reads from /test_data<br/>(local filesystem)
        loop For each evaluation prompt
            Pod->>Inference: POST /v1/completions<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
            Inference-->>Pod: Completions
        end
        Note over Pod: Job exits
    end
